        <br>Welcome to my journey in tech!<br>Youâ€™ll find projects, ideas, snippets. Sometimes curated, sometimes raw, as a simple note to myself and maybe helpful to you too.
      </p>
      <div class="space-x-1 flex-row">
        <a
        href={LINKEDIN_HANDLE}
        target="_blank"
        class="text-base inline-flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 py-2 px-3 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 hover:bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-700 dark:hover:bg-neutral-600"
      >
        <MdiLinkedin />
        <span>LinkedIn</span>
      </a>
        <a
          href={GITHUB_HANDLE}
          target="_blank"
          class="text-base inline-flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 py-2 px-3 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 hover:bg-neutral-300 dark:bg-neutral-700 dark:hover:bg-neutral-600"
        >
          <MdiGithub />
